ğŸ” What does @SpringBootApplication actually do?
It is a combination of three annotations:

@SpringBootApplication = 
    @Configuration +
    @EnableAutoConfiguration +
    @ComponentScan
Letâ€™s understand each of them ğŸ‘‡

1ï¸âƒ£ @Configuration
Marks the class as a configuration class â€” meaning it can define Spring beans.

