EntityManager

TransactionManager

3ï¸âƒ£ @ComponentScan
Tells Spring to scan the current package and its subpackages for:

@Component

@Service

@Repository

@Controller

@RestController
and automatically register them as beans in the Spring context.

âœ… Example:
If your main class is in com.hotel.app and you have controllers in com.hotel.app.controller, they will be detected automatically.

If your beans are in a different package, you can specify manually:

